    "shortDescription": "Buy NFTs on Ronin with off-chain payment. EIP-712 signed intents, on-chain delivery by a Keeper.",
    "description": "Ronin Waypoint Intent Aggregator (RWIA) removes the crypto-friction wall for NFT buyers on Ronin. Users sign an EIP-712 intent and pay the Keeper off-chain (fiat or stablecoin). The Keeper, already in possession of the NFT, delivers it on-chain to the user's wallet, paying the gas. The contract enforces signature validity, deadlines and intent-hash uniqueness; upgrades are gated by an on-chain TimelockController so V2 can introduce Chainlink CCIP cross-chain dispatch without state loss.",
